      <title>西班牙总理拟禁止非欧盟公民购房</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/spain-s-premier-aims-to-ban-non-eu-citizens-from-buying-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯将提议禁止欧盟以外的人在该国购买房屋，这是解决住房短缺问题的更广泛尝试的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/spain-s-premier-aims-to-ban-non-eu-citizens-from-buying-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 16:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
