    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克考虑在选举动荡后重组公共债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/mozambique-weighs-restructuring-public-debt-after-vote-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克新任财政部长表示，莫桑比克政府在选举后的动乱中损失了约 420 亿梅蒂卡尔（6.58 亿美元）的收入，该国正考虑重组公共债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/mozambique-weighs-restructuring-public-debt-after-vote-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 13:44:29 GMT</pubDate>
